      "id": "查看集群信息"
    }}>{`查看集群信息`}</h3>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul"><strong parentName="li">{`日志：`}</strong>{` Rancher 可以跟多种主流日志工具集成，您可以设置 `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "/docs/rancher2/logging/2.0.x-2.4.x/project-logging/_index"
